Calendar

Upcoming events in the life and ministry of our church.

Vacation Bible School

July 11-15th. 6:00 - 8:00 PM.

Jul

11

Cow-a-bunga Farm

“We’ve been to three VBS’s in Mattoon this year, including some in much larger churches, and yours is by far the best.” - Mattoon parent from last year.

VBS is always a highlight of the year at Bible Baptist and this year is going to be awesome. Kids will enjoy awesome farm themed crafts, learn exciting new songs, play fun games and most importantly - learn life changing lessons from the Bible.

Some of the features:

  • Each night of VBS will feature a penny offering with the losing team captain getting “hog slopped” at the end of the week.
  • Each night we’ll have a different live farm animal from Bartel’s Family Petting Zoo.
  • Kids will eat awesome themed snacks based on their lessons each night and make farm themed crafts.
  • much, much more.

VBS is for kids 3 and up and parents are always welcome. See you there!
